{"tid":1955907,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林兆彬:無法忘記墓碑上的編號","createTime":"2020-04-02T20:49:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T12:32:23.000Z","uid":36901,"like":31,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"deb081fb15f9c1bcbeeec1de0cbf26e0caa74e92","tid":1955907,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T20:49:06.000Z","msg":"無法忘記墓碑上的編號<br />\n<br />\n撰文: 林兆彬 | 發佈日期: 02.04.20 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n沙嶺公墓是政府專為無人認領屍體而設的墳場，當你去過沙嶺公墓一次，相信你一世都無法忘記這個類似戰場、令人難以呼吸的畫面：一個個黃色頭盔擺放於細小的墓碑前，一束束向手足致敬的鮮花，冰冷的灰色石塊上沒有人名和相片，亡魂化作無情的年份和編號。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_新聞/hk-discuss/2020/04/墓碑-沙嶺公墓-20200402110129_1f1e_small.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2020%2F04%2F%E5%A2%93%E7%A2%91-%E6%B2%99%E5%B6%BA%E5%85%AC%E5%A2%93-20200402110129_1f1e_small.jpg&h=41fad929&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林兆彬攝<br />\n<br />\n4月1日早上，我與數名油尖旺區議員把3月31日晚太子站外的鮮花運送到沙嶺公墓拜祭。<span style=\"color: red;\">2019年的墓碑數量有165個，而2020年只過了三個月，就已經有113個墓碑，沒有人會相信這是一件正常的事情吧？</span><br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n自由如空氣，只有窒息時才會察覺它的存在。今時今日，連最溫和的獻花權利都可以被政權剝奪，沒有什麼是不可能的。自反送中運動以來，浮屍數量大增，究竟當中有多少是「被自殺」，無人會知。我只知道，假若我們忘記沙嶺公墓墓碑上的編號，就會對不起已犧牲的手足。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_新聞/hk-discuss/2020/04/沙嶺公墓-墓碑-20200402110050_2962_small.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2020%2F04%2F%E6%B2%99%E5%B6%BA%E5%85%AC%E5%A2%93-%E5%A2%93%E7%A2%91-20200402110050_2962_small.jpg&h=e29b54a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林兆彬攝<br />\n<br />\n清明節將至，相信有不少人會前往沙嶺公墓拜祭。去過沙嶺公墓，你就擁有多一份責任，因為你比其他人更接近逝去的手足。在往後的人生中，你必須守護記憶，為他們走下去，還他們一個公道，直到最後一人。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n願死者安息。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/28500/沙嶺公墓-清明節-28501/清明節\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F28500%2F%E6%B2%99%E5%B6%BA%E5%85%AC%E5%A2%93-%E6%B8%85%E6%98%8E%E7%AF%80-28501%2F%E6%B8%85%E6%98%8E%E7%AF%80&d=M80n4YL9TfmCcvG0giRsMoMLxsd%2B2XAbZoZSjzCx9%2B0%3D&h=9aabda54\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/28500/沙嶺公墓-清明節-28501/清明節</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e38e9e2d77b421e0a4317e843167773de59f4992","tid":1955907,"uid":134563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T20:51:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b520576e4538af4093313dfea27c9b7eac953c5","tid":1955907,"uid":20867,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T20:56:19.000Z","msg":"林兆。。。波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0079337795eb809771dfcf6de75ec62302ff4900","tid":1955907,"uid":326195,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T20:56:30.000Z","msg":"其實就算係唔係手足都好，真心希望每一位葬喺公墓嘅人可以安息，連身故都冇人知係邊個其實真係好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12affe5cddbbce80f9638f0fddc83c9910f9c6af","tid":1955907,"uid":178800,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9b520576e4538af4093313dfea27c9b7eac953c5","tid":1955907,"uid":20867,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T20:56:19.000Z","msg":"林兆。。。波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T21:35:15.000Z","msg":"我都係,睇錯待首夫人"},{"pid":"70b11671e0ae98462b001018aabc37547478f69a","tid":1955907,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T21:38:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a74f13bb40fee03e9bf58270602ea3bf7451497","tid":1955907,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":1,"scor